                <li><a href="/blog">Blog</a></li>
                <li><a href="/quienes-somos">Nosotros</a></li>
                <li><a href="/contacto">Contacto</a></li>
                <li><a href="#" class="btn btn-outline" onclick="openModal('loginModal')">Iniciar Sesión</a></li>
                <li><a href="#" class="btn btn-primary" onclick="openModal('registerModal')">Crear Cuenta</a></li>
            </ul>
        </nav>
    </header>

    <!-- Enhanced Page Header -->
    <section style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%); color: white; padding: 8rem 0; position: relative; overflow: hidden;">
        <div style="position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; bottom: 0; background: url('/images/OIP.webp') center/cover; opacity: 0.15;"></div>
        <div class="container text-center" style="position: relative; z-index: 2;">
            <div style="background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1); color: white; padding: 0.5rem 1.5rem; border-radius: 50px; display: inline-block; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; backdrop-filter: blur(10px); font-weight: 600;">
                <span class="material-symbols-outlined" style="font-size: 1.2rem; vertical-align: middle; margin-right: 0.5rem;">chat</span>
                Estamos aquí para ayudarte
            </div>
            <h1 style="font-size: 4rem; margin-bottom: 2rem; font-weight: bold; text-shadow: 0 2px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);">Contacto</h1>
            <p style="font-size: 1.4rem; opacity: 0.95; max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto; line-height: 1.6; text-shadow: 0 1px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);">Tu journey educativo comienza aquí. Conéctate con nuestro equipo de expertos y descubre cómo podemos transformar tu futuro profesional.</p>
            <div style="margin-top: 3rem; display: flex; gap: 2rem; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap;">
                <div style="text-align: center;">
                    <div style="font-size: 2.5rem; font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">24/7</div>
                    <div style="font-size: 1rem; opacity: 0.9;">Soporte Online</div>
                </div>
                <div style="text-align: center;">
                    <div style="font-size: 2.5rem; font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">&lt;1hr</div>
                    <div style="font-size: 1rem; opacity: 0.9;">Tiempo de Respuesta</div>
                </div>
                <div style="text-align: center;">
                    <div style="font-size: 2.5rem; font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">98%</div>
                    <div style="font-size: 1rem; opacity: 0.9;">Satisfacción</div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Enhanced Contact Section -->
    <section class="container mb-3" style="padding: 5rem 0;">
        <div class="text-center mb-3">
            <h2 style="color: #333; font-size: 2.5rem; font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 1rem;">Conéctate con Nosotros</h2>
            <p style="color: #666; font-size: 1.2rem; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto;">Estamos listos para responder todas tus preguntas y ayudarte a comenzar tu journey educativo</p>
        </div>
        <div class="grid grid-2" style="gap: 3rem;">
            <!-- Enhanced Contact Form -->
            <div>
                <div class="contact-form-card" style="background: white; border-radius: 20px; padding: 3rem; box-shadow: 0 15px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); position: relative; overflow: hidden;">
                    <div style="position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; height: 4px; background: linear-gradient(90deg, #667eea, #764ba2);"></div>
                    <div style="margin-bottom: 2rem;">
                        <div style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%); color: white; padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem; border-radius: 50px; display: inline-block; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 1rem;">
                            <span class="material-symbols-outlined" style="font-size: 1.2rem; vertical-align: middle; margin-right: 0.5rem;">edit_note</span>
                            Envíanos un Mensaje
                        </div>
                        <h3 style="color: #333; font-size: 1.8rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; font-weight: bold;">¿Cómo podemos ayudarte?</h3>
                        <p style="color: #666; font-size: 1rem;">Completa el formulario y te responderemos en menos de 1 hora</p>
                    </div>
                    <form id="contactForm" style="">
                        <div class="form-row" style="gap: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
                            <div class="form-group" style="flex: 1;">
                                <label class="form-label" style="color: #333; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; display: block;">Nombre Completo *</label>
                                <div style="position: relative;">
                                    <input type="text" name="nombre" class="form-control" required placeholder="Juan Pérez" style="background: #f8f9fa; border: 2px solid #e9ecef; border-radius: 10px; padding: 1rem 1rem 1rem 3rem; transition: all 0.3s ease;">
                                    <div style="position: absolute; left: 1rem; top: 50%; transform: translateY(-50%); color: #667eea; font-size: 1.2rem;">
                                        <span class="material-symbols-outlined">person</span>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="form-group" style="flex: 1;">
                                <label class="form-label" style="color: #333; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; display: block;">Correo Electrónico *</label>
                                <div style="position: relative;">
                                    <input type="email" name="email" class="form-control" required placeholder="juan@email.com" style="background: #f8f9fa; border: 2px solid #e9ecef; border-radius: 10px; padding: 1rem 1rem 1rem 3rem; transition: all 0.3s ease;">
                                    <div style="position: absolute; left: 1rem; top: 50%; transform: translateY(-50%); color: #667eea; font-size: 1.2rem;">
                                        <span class="material-symbols-outlined">email</span>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="form-row" style="gap: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
                            <div class="form-group" style="flex: 1;">
                                <label class="form-label" style="color: #333; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; display: block;">Teléfono</label>
                                <div style="position: relative;">
                                    <input type="tel" name="telefono" class="form-control" placeholder="+58 414-123-4567" style="background: #f8f9fa; border: 2px solid #e9ecef; border-radius: 10px; padding: 1rem 1rem 1rem 3rem; transition: all 0.3s ease;">
                                    <div style="position: absolute; left: 1rem; top: 50%; transform: translateY(-50%); color: #667eea; font-size: 1.2rem;">
                                        <span class="material-symbols-outlined">phone</span>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="form-group" style="flex: 1;">
                                <label class="form-label" style="color: #333; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; display: block;">Asunto *</label>
                                <div style="position: relative;">
                                    <select name="asunto" class="form-control" required style="background: #f8f9fa; border: 2px solid #e9ecef; border-radius: 10px; padding: 1rem 1rem 1rem 3rem; transition: all 0.3s ease; appearance: none; cursor: pointer;">
                                        <option value="">Selecciona un asunto</option>
                                        <option value="soporte">
                                            <span class="material-symbols-outlined" style="font-size: 1rem; vertical-align: middle; margin-right: 0.5rem;">build</span>
                                            Soporte Técnico
                                        </option>
                                        <option value="ventas">
                                            <span class="material-symbols-outlined" style="font-size: 1rem; vertical-align: middle; margin-right: 0.5rem;">payments</span>
                                            Ventas y Planes
                                        </option>
                                        <option value="academico">
                                            <span class="material-symbols-outlined" style="font-size: 1rem; vertical-align: middle; margin-right: 0.5rem;">school</span>
                                            Consultas Académicas
                                        </option>
                                        <option value="partnership">
                                            <span class="material-symbols-outlined" style="font-size: 1rem; vertical-align: middle; margin-right: 0.5rem;">handshake</span>
                                            Alianzas Estratégicas
                                        </option>
                                        <option value="general">
                                            <span class="material-symbols-outlined" style="font-size: 1rem; vertical-align: middle; margin-right: 0.5rem;">chat</span>
                                            Consulta General
                                        </option>
                                    </select>
                                    <div style="position: absolute; left: 1rem; top: 50%; transform: translateY(-50%); color: #667eea; font-size: 1.2rem;">
                                        <span class="material-symbols-outlined">list_alt</span>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="form-group" style="margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
                            <label class="form-label" style="color: #333; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; display: block;">Mensaje *</label>
                            <div style="position: relative;">
                                <textarea name="mensaje" class="form-control" rows="5" required placeholder="Describe tu consulta o solicitud en detalle..." style="background: #f8f9fa; border: 2px solid #e9ecef; border-radius: 10px; padding: 1rem 1rem 1rem 3rem; transition: all 0.3s ease; resize: vertical;"></textarea>
                                <div style="position: absolute; left: 1rem; top: 1rem; color: #667eea; font-size: 1.2rem;">
                                    <span class="material-symbols-outlined">chat</span>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="form-group" style="margin-bottom: 2rem;">
                            <label style="display: flex; align-items: center; cursor: pointer; padding: 1rem; background: #f8f9fa; border-radius: 10px; border: 2px solid transparent; transition: all 0.3s ease;" onmouseover="this.style.borderColor='#667eea'" onmouseout="this.style.borderColor='transparent'">
                                <input type="checkbox" name="newsletter" style="margin-right: 1rem; width: 20px; height: 20px; accent-color: #667eea;">
                                <span style="color: #333; font-size: 1rem;">Deseo recibir información sobre nuevos cursos y ofertas especiales</span>
                            </label>
                        </div>
                        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary" style="width: 100%; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%); color: white; padding: 1rem 2rem; border: none; border-radius: 12px; font-weight: 600; font-size: 1.1rem; transition: all 0.3s ease; box-shadow: 0 5px 20px rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.3);" onmouseover="this.style.transform='translateY(-2px)'" onmouseout="this.style.transform='translateY(0)'">
                            <span class="material-symbols-outlined" style="font-size: 1.2rem; vertical-align: middle; margin-right: 0.5rem;">send</span>
                            Enviar Mensaje
                        </button>
                    </form>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Enhanced Contact Information -->
            <div>
                <div class="contact-info-card" style="background: white; border-radius: 20px; padding: 3rem; box-shadow: 0 15px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); position: relative; overflow: hidden; margin-bottom: 2rem;">
                    <div style="position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; height: 4px; background: linear-gradient(90deg, #28a745, #20c997);"></div>
                    <div style="margin-bottom: 2rem;">
                        <div style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #28a745 0%, #20c997 100%); color: white; padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem; border-radius: 50px; display: inline-block; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 1rem;">
                            <span class="material-symbols-outlined" style="font-size: 1.2rem; vertical-align: middle; margin-right: 0.5rem;">call</span>
                            Información de Contacto
                        </div>
                        <h3 style="color: #333; font-size: 1.8rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; font-weight: bold;">Múltiples Vías de Contacto</h3>
                        <p style="color: #666; font-size: 1rem;">Elige la opción que mejor se adapte a tus necesidades</p>
                    </div>
                    <div style="margin-bottom: 2rem;">
                        <div class="contact-item" style="display: flex; align-items: center; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; padding: 1.5rem; background: #f8f9fa; border-radius: 15px; border-left: 4px solid #667eea; transition: all 0.3s ease;" onmouseover="this.style.transform='translateX(5px)'" onmouseout="this.style.transform='translateX(0)'">
                            <div style="width: 50px; height: 50px; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%); color: white; border-radius: 50%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; margin-right: 1.5rem; font-size: 1.5rem; box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.3);">
                                <span class="material-symbols-outlined">email</span>
                            </div>
                            <div style="flex: 1;">
                                <strong style="color: #333; font-size: 1.1rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; display: block;">Correo Electrónico</strong>
                                <div style="color: #666; margin-bottom: 0.25rem; font-size: 0.95rem;">info@educonecta.edu.ve</div>
                                <div style="color: #666; font-size: 0.95rem;">soporte@educonecta.edu.ve</div>
                                <div style="background: rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.1); color: #667eea; padding: 0.25rem 0.75rem; border-radius: 20px; font-size: 0.8rem; font-weight: 600; display: inline-block; margin-top: 0.5rem;">Respuesta en &lt;1hr</div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="contact-item" style="display: flex; align-items: center; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; padding: 1.5rem; background: #f8f9fa; border-radius: 15px; border-left: 4px solid #28a745; transition: all 0.3s ease;" onmouseover="this.style.transform='translateX(5px)'" onmouseout="this.style.transform='translateX(0)'">
                            <div style="width: 50px; height: 50px; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #28a745 0%, #20c997 100%); color: white; border-radius: 50%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; margin-right: 1.5rem; font-size: 1.5rem; box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(40, 167, 69, 0.3);">
                                <span class="material-symbols-outlined">phone</span>
                            </div>
                            <div style="flex: 1;">
                                <strong style="color: #333; font-size: 1.1rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; display: block;">Teléfono</strong>
                                <div style="color: #666; margin-bottom: 0.25rem; font-size: 0.95rem;">+58 414-123-4567</div>
                                <div style="color: #666; font-size: 0.95rem;">+58 212-123-4567</div>
                                <div style="background: rgba(40, 167, 69, 0.1); color: #28a745; padding: 0.25rem 0.75rem; border-radius: 20px; font-size: 0.8rem; font-weight: 600; display: inline-block; margin-top: 0.5rem;">Lunes a Sábado</div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="contact-item" style="display: flex; align-items: center; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; padding: 1.5rem; background: #f8f9fa; border-radius: 15px; border-left: 4px solid #ffc107; transition: all 0.3s ease;" onmouseover="this.style.transform='translateX(5px)'" onmouseout="this.style.transform='translateX(0)'">
                            <div style="width: 50px; height: 50px; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ffc107 0%, #ff8f00 100%); color: white; border-radius: 50%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; margin-right: 1.5rem; font-size: 1.5rem; box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(255, 193, 7, 0.3);">
                                <span class="material-symbols-outlined">location_on</span>
                            </div>
                            <div style="flex: 1;">
                                <strong style="color: #333; font-size: 1.1rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; display: block;">Dirección</strong>
                                <div style="color: #666; margin-bottom: 0.25rem; font-size: 0.95rem;">Edificio Torre Educativa, Piso 8</div>
                                <div style="color: #666; margin-bottom: 0.25rem; font-size: 0.95rem;">Av. Libertador, Caracas 1010</div>
                                <div style="color: #666; font-size: 0.95rem;">Venezuela</div>
                                <div style="background: rgba(255, 193, 7, 0.1); color: #ffc107; padding: 0.25rem 0.75rem; border-radius: 20px; font-size: 0.8rem; font-weight: 600; display: inline-block; margin-top: 0.5rem;">Visitas con cita</div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="contact-item" style="display: flex; align-items: center; padding: 1.5rem; background: #f8f9fa; border-radius: 15px; border-left: 4px solid #dc3545; transition: all 0.3s ease;" onmouseover="this.style.transform='translateX(5px)'" onmouseout="this.style.transform='translateX(0)'">
                            <div style="width: 50px; height: 50px; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #dc3545 0%, #c82333 100%); color: white; border-radius: 50%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; margin-right: 1.5rem; font-size: 1.5rem; box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(220, 53, 69, 0.3);">
                                <span class="material-symbols-outlined">schedule</span>
                            </div>
                            <div style="flex: 1;">
                                <strong style="color: #333; font-size: 1.1rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; display: block;">Horario de Atención</strong>
                                <div style="color: #666; margin-bottom: 0.25rem; font-size: 0.95rem;">Lunes a Viernes: 9:00 AM - 6:00 PM</div>
                                <div style="color: #666; font-size: 0.95rem;">Sábados: 10:00 AM - 2:00 PM</div>
                                <div style="background: rgba(220, 53, 69, 0.1); color: #dc3545; padding: 0.25rem 0.75rem; border-radius: 20px; font-size: 0.8rem; font-weight: 600; display: inline-block; margin-top: 0.5rem;">Soporte 24/7 Online</div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Enhanced Quick Support -->
                <div class="quick-support-card" style="background: white; border-radius: 20px; padding: 3rem; box-shadow: 0 15px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); position: relative; overflow: hidden;">
                    <div style="position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; height: 4px; background: linear-gradient(90deg, #ffc107, #ff8f00);"></div>
                    <div style="margin-bottom: 2rem;">
                        <div style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ffc107 0%, #ff8f00 100%); color: white; padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem; border-radius: 50px; display: inline-block; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 1rem;">
                            <span class="material-symbols-outlined" style="font-size: 1.2rem; vertical-align: middle; margin-right: 0.5rem;">bolt</span>
                            Soporte Rápido
                        </div>
                        <h3 style="color: #333; font-size: 1.8rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; font-weight: bold;">Ayuda Instantánea</h3>
                        <p style="color: #666; font-size: 1rem;">Resuelve tus dudas rápidamente con nuestras opciones de autosoporte</p>
                    </div>
                    <div style="display: grid; gap: 1rem;">
                        <div class="support-option" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f8f9fa 0%, #e9ecef 100%); padding: 1.5rem; border-radius: 15px; border-left: 4px solid #667eea; transition: all 0.3s ease; cursor: pointer;" onmouseover="this.style.transform='translateX(5px)'" onmouseout="this.style.transform='translateX(0)'" onclick="window.open('/faq', '_blank')">
                            <div style="display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between;">
                                <div>
                                    <h4 style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem; color: #333; font-weight: bold; font-size: 1.1rem;">
                                        <span class="material-symbols-outlined" style="font-size: 1.2rem; vertical-align: middle; margin-right: 0.5rem; color: #667eea;">build</span>
                                        ¿Necesitas ayuda técnica?
                                    </h4>
                                    <p style="color: #666; font-size: 0.9rem; margin-bottom: 0;">Revisa nuestra sección de preguntas frecuentes</p>
                                </div>
                                <div style="background: #667eea; color: white; width: 40px; height: 40px; border-radius: 50%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 1.2rem; box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.3);">→</div>
